'''黑斯堡'''（{{lang-en|'''Happisburgh'''}} {{IPAc-en|audio=En-Happisburgh.ogg|'|h|eɪ|z|.|b|3r|@}} {{respell|HAYZ|bur-ə}}）是[[英國|英國]][[諾福克郡|諾福克郡]]的一個村莊及[[民政教區|民政教區]]。有沿海的[[B1159公路|B1159公路]]通過。<ref name=osexp252>Ordnance Survey (2002). ''OS Explorer Map 252 - Norfolk Coast East''. ISBN 0-319-21888-0.</ref>

2010年在黑斯堡發現了八十萬年前的人類燧石工具，這是英國最古老的人類存在的證據。<ref name="nature.com">{{cite web |author=Miriam Frankel |url=http://www.nature.com/news/2010/100707/full/news.2010.338.html |title=Early Britons could cope with cold : Nature News |publisher=Nature.com |date= |accessdate=13 November 2012 |archive-date=2014-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308112135/http://www.nature.com/news/2010/100707/full/news.2010.338.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2013年5月一系列[[黑斯堡足跡|黑斯堡足跡]]也發現於黑斯堡的沙灘上。<ref name=bbc7feb14 />

黑斯堡民政教區的面積為{{convert|10.78|km2|abbr=on}}，不過由於海岸侵蝕的緣故，正在不斷縮小。根據[[2010年英國人口普查|2010年英國人口普查]]，黑斯堡有607戶共1,372位居民。<ref name=osnncc>Office for National Statistics & Norfolk County Council (2001). ''[http://www.norfolk.gov.uk/consumption/groups/public/documents/general_resources/ncc017867.xls Census population and household counts for unparished urban areas and all parishes] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5hgXE2a2B?url=http://www.norfolk.gov.uk/consumption/groups/public/documents/general_resources/ncc017867.xls |date=20090621010005 |dateformat=iso }}''. Retrieved 2 December 2005.</ref>

==歷史==

